sqlQuery1: SELECT SUM(FTE) AS Sum_of_FTE FROM TGT.VW_ONEDATA_OFFSHORE_ONSITE AS OffshoreOnsite_Dossier JOIN TGT.VW_FACT_RESOURCE_REQUEST_DETAIL AS Fact_Resource_Request_Detail ON OffshoreOnsite_Dossier.Resource_Request_Detail_Key = Fact_Resource_Request_Detail.Resource_Request_Detail_Key WHERE OffshoreOnsite_Dossier.OFFSHORE_ONSITE_FLAG = 'Offshore' AND OffshoreOnsite_Dossier.[Allocation Subgroup] = 'Billable' AND OffshoreOnsite_Dossier.[Is Active?] <> 'N' AND OffshoreOnsite_Dossier.[Weekly/monthly/both] = 'Monthly' AND OffshoreOnsite_Dossier.[As of date] = (SELECT MAX([As of date]) FROM TGT.VW_ONEDATA_OFFSHORE_ONSITE) AND Fact_Resource_Request_Detail.BILLABILITY_START_DATE >= '2010-01-01';
sqlQuery2: SELECT SUM(FTE) AS Sum_of_FTE FROM TGT.VW_ONEDATA_OFFSHORE_ONSITE AS OffshoreOnsite_Dossier WHERE OffshoreOnsite_Dossier.level_group <> 'INT' AND OffshoreOnsite_Dossier.[Allocation group2] = 'Investments' AND OffshoreOnsite_Dossier.[Is Active?] <> 'N' AND OffshoreOnsite_Dossier.[Weekly/monthly/both] = 'Monthly' AND OffshoreOnsite_Dossier.[As of date] = (SELECT MAX([As of date]) FROM TGT.VW_ONEDATA_OFFSHORE_ONSITE);
sqlQuery3: SELECT SUM(FTE) AS Sum_of_FTE FROM TGT.VW_ONEDATA_OFFSHORE_ONSITE AS OffshoreOnsite_Dossier WHERE OffshoreOnsite_Dossier.level_group <> 'INT' AND OffshoreOnsite_Dossier.[Allocation group2] = 'Available' AND OffshoreOnsite_Dossier.[Is Active?] <> 'N' AND OffshoreOnsite_Dossier.[Weekly/monthly/both] = 'Monthly' AND OffshoreOnsite_Dossier.OFFSHORE_ONSITE_FLAG = 'offshore' AND OffshoreOnsite_Dossier.[As of date] = (SELECT MIN(MAX_DATE) FROM (SELECT MAX([As of date]) AS MAX_DATE FROM TGT.VW_ONEDATA_OFFSHORE_ONSITE UNION ALL SELECT MAX([Ref_Dt]) AS MAX_DATE FROM TGT.VW_FACT_INSIGHTS) AS MaxDates);
sqlQuery4: SELECT SUM(FTE) as Sum_of_FTE FROM TGT.VW_ONEDATA_OFFSHORE_ONSITE WHERE [Weekly/monthly/both] = 'Monthly' AND ([Level_Group] <> 'INT' OR [Level_Group] IS NULL) AND [Is Active?] <> 'N' AND [OFFSHORE_ONSITE_FLAG] = 'offshore' AND [As of date] = (SELECT MAX([As of date]) FROM TGT.VW_ONEDATA_OFFSHORE_ONSITE);
sqlQuery5: SELECT SUM(EBHC_DOSSIER) as sum_of_ebhc FROM TGT.VW_FACT_INSIGHTS WHERE Ref_Dt = (SELECT MAX(Ref_Dt) FROM TGT.VW_FACT_INSIGHTS);
